In [16]:
def getCorrWithPM2dot5(df,items):
    corrMethodList=['spearman','pearson']
    corrSeriesList=[]
    for corrMethod in corrMethodList:
        tempList=[]
        for item in items:
            corrVal=df['PM2dot5'].corr(df[item], method=corrMethod)
            tempList.append(corrVal)     
        corrSeriesList.append(pd.Series(tempList))
    corrDf=pd.DataFrame(corrSeriesList)
    corrDf.columns=items
    corrDf.index=map(normalize,corrMethodList)
    return corrDf

getCorrWithPM2dot5(df,df.columns[3:8].tolist())

def chooseDataset(isRaw):
    if isRaw:
        X=df.drop(columns=['PM2dot5','clf','index']).values
        y=df['PM2dot5'].values
    else:
        X=df.drop(columns=['clf','index']).iloc[:-1,:].values
        y=df['PM2dot5'][1:].values
    return (X,y)

def kFoldCVTest(modelName,estiList,X,y):
    kFoldTimes=5
    kf = KFold(n_splits=kFoldTimes, shuffle=True, random_state=None)
    kf_split=kf.split(X)
    model=modelDict[modelName]
    modelEstiList=[]
    for train_index, test_index in kf_split:
        # 训练模型 
        
        start =time.clock()
        model.fit(X[train_index,:], y[train_index])
        end = time.clock()
        
        useTime=end-start
        # 对测试集进行预测
        prediction = model.predict(X[test_index,:])
        actual=y[test_index]
        

#         modelEsti=[r2_score(actual,prediction),mean_squared_error(actual,prediction)]
#         modelEstiList.append(modelEsti)
        modelEsti=[]
        for estiName in estiList:
            exec('temp={}(actual,prediction)'.format(estiName))
            modelEsti.append(temp)
        modelEsti.append(useTime)
        modelEstiList.append(modelEsti)
        
    estiDf=pd.DataFrame(modelEstiList)
    

    
    meanSeries=estiDf.apply(np.mean)
    meanSeries.name='平均值'
    estiDf=estiDf.append(meanSeries)
    
    estiDf.columns=estiList+['计时(s)']
    return estiDf
In [28]:
def getCVMeanList(list,estiList,X,y):
    meanDf=pd.DataFrame()
    for item in list:
        tempDf=kFoldCVTest(item,estiList,X,y)
        tempSeries=tempDf.loc['平均值']
        tempSeries.name=item
        meanDf=meanDf.append(tempSeries)
    return meanDf

def splitDataset(X,y):
    X_train_raw, X_test_raw, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(X, y, test_size=0.2, random_state=0)
    X_train=X_train_raw[:,1:]
    X_train_date=X_train_raw[:,0]
    X_test=X_test_raw[:,1:]
    X_test_date=X_test_raw[:,0]
    return (X_train,X_train_date,X_test,X_test_date, y_train, y_test)

(X_train,X_train_date,X_test,X_test_date, y_train, y_test)=splitDataset(X,y)

def get_pca_compare_df(start,end,model,estiList):
    pca_compare_df=pd.DataFrame()
    for num in range(start,end):
        pca=PCA(n_components=num)
        X_pca=pca.fit_transform(X[:,1:])
        temp_pca_df=kFoldCVTest(model,estiList,X_pca,y)
        temp_pca_mean=temp_pca_df.loc['平均值']
        temp_pca_mean.name=num
        pca_compare_df=pca_compare_df.append(temp_pca_mean)
    return pca_compare_df

def plot_pca_compare(start,end,model,estiList):
    pca_compare_df=get_pca_compare_df(start,end,model,estiList)
    page=Page()
    plotX=pca_compare_df.index

    for column in pca_compare_df.columns:
        line=Line(column)
        plotY=[round(x,3) for x in pca_compare_df[column].values]
        line.add('', plotX, plotY,is_smooth=True,is_more_utils=True,mark_line=['max','average','min'],xaxis_name='特征个数',yaxis_min='dataMin',yaxis_max='dataMax')
        page.add(line)
    return page

def plotCompare(name,predict):
    line = Line('{}预测值时序图'.format(name))

    dictCompr={'真实值':y_test,'{}预测值'.format(name):predict}
    for (key,val) in dictCompr.items():
        lineDf=pd.DataFrame([X_test_date,val])
        lineDf.index=['date','val']
        lineDf=lineDf.sort_values(by='date',axis=1)
        (plotX,plotY)=(pd.to_datetime(lineDf.iloc[0]),lineDf.iloc[1])
        line.add(key, plotX, plotY,is_smooth=True,is_more_utils=True,is_datazoom_show=True)

    return line

In [36]:
def compareXGBoost(testTimes):
    defaultBetter=0
    
    for _ in range(testTimes):
        CVMeanDf=getCVMeanList(['XGBoost','XGBoost_default'],
                           ['mean_absolute_error','mean_squared_error','mean_squared_log_error','median_absolute_error','r2_score','explained_variance_score'])
        CVMeanDf=CVMeanDf.sort_values(by='mean_squared_error')
        if CVMeanDf.loc['XGBoost_default','mean_squared_error'] < CVMeanDf.loc['XGBoost','mean_squared_error']:
            defaultBetter+=1
    return pd.DataFrame([defaultBetter,testTimes-defaultBetter],index=['默认XGBoost','调优后XGBoost'],columns=['指标胜出的次数'])

In [40]:
def sortImportant(plotX,plotY):
    plotDf=pd.DataFrame([plotX,plotY],index=['plotX','plotY'])
    plotDf=plotDf.sort_values(by='plotY',axis=1)
    return (plotDf.loc['plotX'],plotDf.loc['plotY'])

def hotKeyImportant(rawX,rawY,importantName):
    

    (plotX,plotY)=([],[])

    itemBoolList=rawX.str.contains(importantName)
    for (colomn,itemBool,y) in zip(rawX,itemBoolList,rawY):
        if itemBool:
            plotX.append(colomn)
            plotY.append(y)

    plotDf=pd.DataFrame({'plotX': plotX,'plotY': plotY})
    plotDf['plotX']=plotDf['plotX'].str.split('_').str.get(1)
    plotGrouped=plotDf.groupby(plotDf['plotX'])['plotY']
    
    plotX=plotGrouped.indices.keys()
    plotY=plotGrouped.agg('mean').tolist()
    
    return sortImportant(plotX,plotY)

def hotKeyImportantPlot(rawX,rawY,importantName,title):
    (plotX,plotY)=hotKeyImportant(rawX,rawY,importantName)
    bar = Bar("{}重要性分析".format(title))
    bar.add(title, plotX, plotY,is_convert=True,label_emphasis_pos='inside')
    return bar
